"```sql\nSELECT r.time\nFROM results r\nJOIN races ra ON r.raceId = ra.raceId\nWHERE ra.year = 2008\n  AND ra.name = 'Chinese Grand Prix'\n  AND r.positionOrder = 2;\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the finish time for the driver who ranked second in the 2008 Chinese Grand Prix. It joins the `results` and `races` tables using the `raceId` foreign key and filters the results based on the year, race name, and position order."